<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero-section" style="min-height:350px;" aria-label="Hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"><div class="hero-overlay"></div></div>
  <div class="container hero-content" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;min-height:350px;padding:3rem 24px;">
    <div class="hero-text" style="text-align:center;align-items:center;">
      <h1 class="hero-title" style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 1rem;"><%= page.heroTitle %></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle"><%= page.heroSubtitle %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
<section class="section-pad">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
    <div class="rich-content">
      <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 2026</p>
      <p>PestControlNearMe ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website <strong>www.pestcontrolnearme.in</strong> or use our pest control services.</p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>Personal Information</h3>
      <p>We may collect the following personal information when you contact us, book a service, or fill out a form on our website:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Full name</li>
        <li>Phone number</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Property address (for service delivery)</li>
        <li>Type of pest problem</li>
        <li>Preferred service date and time</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
      <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>IP address and browser type</li>
        <li>Device information and operating system</li>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent on our website</li>
        <li>Referring website or search terms</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide and schedule pest control services</li>
        <li>Respond to your enquiries and service requests</li>
        <li>Send appointment confirmations and service reminders</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        <li>Send promotional offers (only with your consent)</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Our certified pest control technicians (for service delivery only)</li>
        <li>Payment processors (for secure transaction handling)</li>
        <li>Legal authorities (if required by law)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information, including SSL encryption, secure servers, and restricted access to personal data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>Our website may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies help us understand how visitors use our website and enable us to improve our services. You can disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal information</li>
        <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
        <li>Request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to read their privacy policies.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+919453394533"><%= phone %></a></li>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:<%= email %>"><%= email %></a></li>
        <li>Address: Mumbai, Maharashtra – 400001, India</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
